{"tid":2498158,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何君堯辦事處遭破壞 律政司兩度追擊亞氏保加症男生 終由感化令變入教導所","createTime":"2021-04-21T03:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T10:33:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"74d13370ede84ef89444a126280c710adb9732e2","tid":2498158,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NYmoKiiVqcsCPc9vmP1JYd_0TFs=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B2VZGZBB7ZCFPGESALS7DKTSBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNYmoKiiVqcsCPc9vmP1JYd_0TFs%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB2VZGZBB7ZCFPGESALS7DKTSBQ.jpg&h=e351d081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前年7.21白衣人事件翌日，大批市民到立法會議員何君堯位於荃灣的辦事處大肆破壞。患有過度活躍和亞氏保加症的涉案男學生早前承認刑事毀壞罪，裁判官溫紹明原本判處男生接受感化一年，及後經律政司覆核，改判200小時社會服務令。惟律政司仍然不滿，早前向上訴庭申請覆核刑罰，上訴庭認為裁判官原則上犯錯，應改判拘禁式刑罰。上訴庭索閱男生的多份懲教院所報告後，今改判男生進入教導所，理由擇日以書面頒佈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210421/JSFBDMAMHRDVRJ3LKWE7HEOCHE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210421%2FJSFBDMAMHRDVRJ3LKWE7HEOCHE%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dE4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=4681d53c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210421%2FJSFBDMAMHRDVRJ3LKWE7HEOCHE%2F&h=6132ffd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210421/JSFBDMAMHRDVRJ3LKWE7HEOCHE/</a>"},{"pid":"86329890222a18e5dff7d251f43b10691398d05a","tid":2498158,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\"